lead_paragraph: Finally, some good news for the scuffling Chicago Bears: Quarterback Jay Cutler will return from a thumb injury to play against the Minnesota Vikings on Oct. 31.

headline.print_headline: QB Jay Cutler Receives Medical Clearance to Play for Bears
